# Snapshot Governance Vote Bot

## Environment Variables

| Variable | Required | Description |
|----------|----------|-------------|
| `GOVBOT_PRIVATE_KEY` | Yes | Private key for signing votes (EIP-712) |
| `GOVBOT_WALLET` | Yes | Wallet address that holds voting power |
| `GOVBOT_SNAPSHOT_HUB` | No | GraphQL endpoint (default: https://hub.snapshot.org/graphql) |

## Quick Start

1. Copy `config.json` and edit spaces/rules
2. Set env vars or paste keys into `config.json`
3. `pip install -r requirements.txt`
4. `python governance_bot.py`

## One-off Commands

```bash
# List active proposals for a space
python governance_bot.py --list-proposals aave.eth

# Single poll cycle (good for cron)
python governance_bot.py --once
```
